\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

\f1\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 Conclusion\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f0\b0\fs24 \cf0 A 12-week intermittent fasting regimen is effective in improving glycemic control, reducing body weight, and favorably modifying lipid profile in adults with T2D. Time-restricted fasting appears safe, feasible, and may serve as a practical adjunct to standard dietary management. Long-term studies are warranted to determine sustained benefits and broader applicability in diverse populations.\
